title: desk top toys funny little app
description:
I&#039;ve had this since win95 days and now I got XP Pro SP2 and it has worked on everything

when you click the DTTY3200.EXE a box will pop up with "toys" all around it.
click any toy and see what happens. the "toy" may erase your screen or 
"break it"....  DON&#039;T PANIC... these are TOYS.....
hit the ESC key and the box reappears, left click the box and exit, all goes back to normal.

this is not an install, just click and play.

enjoy
